snippet.title: Cherry Creek Puzzle Game Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Cherry Creek is a tile-turning puzzle game, set in a picturesque natural environment.  The aim is to rotate the river tiles to take water from the fountain to all the cherry trees.

Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1018990/Cherry_Creek/

Itch:
https://seconddimension.itch.io/cherry-creek
